    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>The Cause of God May Be Reproached</strong>&mdash;The world has a right to expect strict integrity in those who profess to be Bible Christians. By one man&apos;s indifference in regard to paying his just dues all our people are in danger of being regarded as unreliable.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">8<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"5T 179.1\" data-link=\"113.903\">Testimonies for the Church 5:179</span>.</span></a></sup>",
