    "content": "Those who make any pretensions to godliness should adorn the doctrine they profess, and not give occasion for the truth to be reviled through their inconsiderate course of action. &ldquo;Owe no man any thing,&rdquo; says the apostle.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">9<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"5T 181.4\" data-link=\"113.913\">Ibid., 5:181, 182</span>.</span></a></sup>",
